  "texts": [
    "Therein, NNs are used to predict adjustments to quadrature weights and positions from the nodal positions to improve the accuracy for distorted elements.",
    "Similarly, NNs have been applied as correction for strain-displacement matrices for distorted elements [430].NNs have also been employed to provide improved gradient estimates.",
    "Specifically, [431] modify the gradient computation to match a fine scale simulation on a coarse grid:∂ n u ∂ x n ≈ i α (n) i u i.",
    "(62)The coefficients α i are predicted by NNs from the current coarse solution.",
    "Special constraints are imposed on α i to guarantee accurate derivatives."
